     fhir:Narrative.div "<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><p class=\"res-header-id\"><b>Generated Narrative: ValueSet RevisionIndikationDKR</b></p><a name=\"RevisionIndikationDKR\"> </a><a name=\"hcRevisionIndikationDKR\"> </a><p>This value set includes codes based on the following rules:</p><ul><li>Include these codes as defined in <a href=\"CodeSystem-RevisionIndication.html\"><code>https://kip.rkkp.dk/fhir/CodeSystem/RevisionIndication</code></a><span title=\"Version is not explicitly stated, which means it is fixed to the version provided in this specification\"> version ?2.23.1</span><table class=\"none\"><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>Display</b></td><td><b>Definition</b></td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-RevisionIndication.html#RevisionIndication-second_part_two_stage_revision\">second_part_two_stage_revision</a></td><td>2. del af 2-stadie revision</td><td>2. del af 2-stadie revision</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-RevisionIndication.html#RevisionIndication-aseptic_solution\">aseptic_solution</a></td><td>Aseptisk løsning</td><td>Aseptisk løsning</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-RevisionIndication.html#RevisionIndication-pain\">pain</a></td><td>Smerter uden løsning</td><td>Pain / Smerter</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-RevisionIndication.html#RevisionIndication-instability\">instability</a></td><td>Instabilitet</td><td>Instabilitet</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-RevisionIndication.html#RevisionIndication-infection\">infection</a></td><td>Dyb infektion (mikrobiologisk verificeret)</td><td>Infection / Infektion</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-RevisionIndication.html#RevisionIndication-suspected_infection\">suspected_infection</a></td><td>Dyb infektion (mistænkt)</td><td>Mistænkt eller manifest infektion</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-RevisionIndication.html#RevisionIndication-secondary_insertion\">secondary_insertion</a></td><td>Sekundær isættelse af patellakomponent</td><td>Sekundær isættelse</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-RevisionIndication.html#RevisionIndication-polyethylene_failure_patella\">polyethylene_failure_patella</a></td><td>Polyetylen-svigt patella</td><td>Polyethylen-svigt (patella)</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-RevisionIndication.html#RevisionIndication-polyethylene_failure_tibia\">polyethylene_failure_tibia</a></td><td>Polyetylen-svigt tibia</td><td>Polyethylen-svigt (tibia)</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-RevisionIndication.html#RevisionIndication-arthrosis_progression\">arthrosis_progression</a></td><td>Progression af artrose</td><td>Athrosis progression / Artrose progression</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-RevisionIndication.html#RevisionIndication-periprosthetic_fracture\">periprosthetic_fracture</a></td><td>Periprostetisk fraktur</td><td>Periprostetisk fraktur</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-RevisionIndication.html#RevisionIndication-malplaced_component\">malplaced_component</a></td><td>Malposition af komponenter</td><td>Malplaceret komponent</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-RevisionIndication.html#RevisionIndication-constrained_mobility\">constrained_mobility</a></td><td>Indskrænket bevægelighed</td><td>Indskrænket bevægelighed</td></tr></table></li><li>Include these codes as defined in <a href=\"CodeSystem-GenericValues.html\"><code>https://kip.rkkp.dk/fhir/CodeSystem/GenericValues</code></a><span title=\"Version is not explicitly stated, which means it is fixed to the version provided in this specification\"> version ?2.23.1</span><table class=\"none\"><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>Display</b></td><td><b>Definition</b></td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-GenericValues.html#GenericValues-other\">other</a></td><td>Andet</td><td>Other - used to choose unspecific value not in a valueset</td></tr></table></li></ul></div>"
